Are you sure it&#39;s a whitespace character on the end? You are splitting on &#39;
&#39;, but many machines use &#39;
&#39; to indicate a new line. If your text file is using &#39;
&#39; then all of your data in the <code>cuv</code> array is actually ending in &#39;&#39;, not in a whitespace. This would also cause your <code>if (a == b)</code> to fail.
